data.description:
Step into a world of potential with this 1959 bungalow, a canvas waiting for your personalized touch. Located in the heart of downtown Lee’s Summit, this home offers the ideal opportunity for both first-time homeowners and those with a keen eye for design and renovation. This classic residence presents an affordable alternative to renting, promising both character and a chance for equity-building with some cosmetic enhancements.

The outside boasts a fully stuccoed exterior and thermal windows. The expansive backyard is an oasis of mature trees offering ample shade, making it perfect for landscaping projects or the addition of a garden. Even enough room to add a shed or garage, if desired. The existing composite deck could become the centerpiece of your outdoor entertainment. 

Inside, the common areas were just repainted and the LVP flooring will provide years of enjoyment. The home comes with all the essential appliances, including the refrigerator and washer/dryer. The basement, vast in size, offers an abundance of storage space.

The prime location is undeniably one of its major selling points. Find yourself just moments away from a variety of downtown dining options and have the convenience of quick access to 470. Be it shopping malls, beautiful parks, local farmers market, or other attractions, everything is within easy reach. Imagine walking the dog up to get coffee on Saturday mornings!
